{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 2143055, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 415758, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "你为啥觉得打击辅导机构是为了减轻家长焦虑？", "timestamp": 1627357945, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2143064, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 415758, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "我觉得还行啊，最顶级的权贵什么政策都没用的，但现在拉低了小资和上不起培训机构的人的差距啊，只要能真正落实", "timestamp": 1627358011, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2143069, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 415758, "reply_to": 2143064, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 但是清华的学生大部分将来是小资吧，属于现在被打压的阶层", "timestamp": 1627358056, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2143074, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 415758, "reply_to": 2143064, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 是拉高了啊，小资可以请家教", "timestamp": 1627358098, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2143084, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 415758, "reply_to": 2143064, "tag": null, "text": "我感觉这么搞以后会出打着兴趣班名义的补习班、还有专门家教的”保姆“", "timestamp": 1627358173, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2143087, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 415758, "reply_to": 2143069, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 那你这就是典型屁股决定立场了", "timestamp": 1627358193, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2143089, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 415758, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "都上清华了，自己教不好吗？", "timestamp": 1627358198, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2143091, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 415758, "reply_to": 2143064, "tag": null, "text": "顺便骂一句禁搜题软件的事情，禁了这玩意也不能让学生认真写作业，无非是从拍一道题抄一道题变成直接抄同学的", "timestamp": 1627358214, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2143097, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 415758, "reply_to": 2143084, "t